text: Every street and every lane, everyone is greeting,  when we meet and say hello, they all greet to " Gongxi ".
GongXi GongXi GongXi ni ya. GongXi GongXi GongXi ni.
Spring time will be coming soon. Bringing us the good news.
Soft warm breeze is blowing. Giving life to good earth.
GongXi GongXi GongXi ni ya. GongXi GongXi GongXi ni.
